source:
TEXT_BANARK128_04578_SEQ_00<tab>Maru reeds a resupply for a bustling business.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANARK128_04578_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>Règle spéciale<var 1D /var>:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
<var 1A 02 /var>Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe ou le job qui a servi à la commencer.<var 1A 01 /var>

Maru a besoin d'aide pour récupérer des ingrédients.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_TODO_00<tab>Place the fragrant fish at the designated locations and slay any Akyaali crabs that appear.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_TODO_00<tab>Utiliser les appâts aux endroits indiqués et vaincre les crabes d'Akyaali à longues pattes

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the Akyaali crab legs to Maru.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_TODO_01<tab>Apporter les pattes de crabe d'Akyaali à Maru

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_000<tab>The meyhane has drawn people of all stripes to our little corner of the realm, and for that I'm grateful. That bein' said, the strain on our supplies grows with every new face, and I need your help to stave off an impendin' shortage.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_000<tab>Nous avons de nombreux clients à la taverne, mais elle est si populaire que nous manquons ré<var 16 /var>gu<var 16 /var>liè<var 16 /var>re<var 16 /var>ment d'ingrédients...

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_001<tab>I'm talkin' about Akyaali crab legs─as popular as they are pointy! Still, the creature that bears 'em should be easy prey for you. I reckon they'll know it, too, so don't be stingy with the bait if you want 'em to come scuttlin'.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_001<tab>J'ai besoin de pattes de crabe d'Akyaali. Utilise <var 33 ((EventItem)) 07F61E91D50202 /var> pour attirer les crabes près de la plage et les vaincre.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_002<tab>Just to be on the safe side, you'd best set down three of these fish, eh? Space 'em out, too, so as to better your chances. Safe huntin', friend.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_002<tab>Par contre, même avec un appât, ils ne se montrent pas toujours... Essaie de les attirer à trois endroits différents, ça devrait être suffisant.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_SYSTEM_000_003<tab>There don't appear to be any hungry crabs in the area.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_SYSTEM_000_003<tab>Il n'y a pas de crabe d'Akyaali à longues pattes par ici...

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_004<tab>Ah, there you are. I hope you had a chance to enjoy the spray of salt water on your face durin' your hunt. Did you get the legs?
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_004<tab>Tu es de retour<var 1D /var>! Tu m'as apporté des pattes de crabe d'Akyaali<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_005<tab>Ah, yes... These are exactly what I was lookin' for. Thank you for bringin' me such fine specimens─we'll feed many a hungry Hippo Rider with these.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_005<tab>C'est bien ça<var 1D /var>! Elles sont assez grosses, en plus<var 1D /var>! Je te remercie.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_006<tab>...An' plenty of visitors besides, no doubt. Not a lot of cooks linin' up to duel those spindly buggers, even if their meat makes for some of the most mouthwaterin' seafood on the island.
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_006<tab>Leurs muscles sont bien développés, donc il y a de quoi se mettre sous la dent. De plus, leur goût est profond<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_007<tab>Toss 'em in a curry and their flavor still sings through the spices, or throw 'em in a biryani for some delightful texture. And that's just the beginnin'...
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_007<tab>Même en les utilisant pour un curry, il n'est pas com<var 16 /var>plè<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment effacé par les épices. Bien sûr, ces pattes sont tout aussi excellentes en biryani.

source: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_008<tab>'Course, if they ain't fresh, they ain't nearly as tasty, so it may not be long before we're needin' more. Until then!
target: TEXT_BANARK128_04578_MARU_000_008<tab>Par contre, comme elle doivent toujours être bien fraîches, il faut aller en chercher dès qu'il en manque... Tu m'as bien aidé, merci<var 1D /var>!
